        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nThis code is not actually ready for review.  However, I wanted to push it up for a design/strategy review.  The key files to examine are: usecases.drl, UsecasesManager.java, and Step2.java.\n\nThere is still a lot of java code, but the control is now in the rules.\n\nThere is still a fair amount of rule/application-specific code - very little is generic, so it appears that organizations would probably have to clone and modify controller-usecases for their specific situations.",
